<para style="q1">

<verse number="21" style="v" />You have done these things, but I have kept silent,</para>

<para style="q1">so you thought that I was someone just like yourself.</para>

<para style="q1">But I will reprove you and bring up, right before your eyes, all the things you have done.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="22" style="v" />Give this careful consideration, you who forget God,</para>

<para style="q1">otherwise I will tear you to pieces,</para>

<para style="q1">and there will be no one to come to help you!</para>
